(271, 'spb_js_templates', 'a:20:{s:27:"global-video-cdn_2141561595";a:2:{s:4:"name";s:16:"global video cdn";s:8:"template";s:2886:"[spb_row wrap_type=\\"full-width\\" parallax_type=\\"color\\" bg_type=\\"cover\\" parallax_video_height=\\"video-height\\" parallax_video_overlay=\\"none\\" parallax_image_height=\\"content-height\\" parallax_image_movement=\\"fixed\\" parallax_image_speed=\\"0.5\\" row_overlay_opacity=\\"0\\" row_padding_vertical=\\"0\\" row_margin_vertical=\\"0\\" remove_element_spacing=\\"no\\" width=\\"1/1\\" el_position=\\"first last\\"] [spb_single_image image=\\"209\\" image_size=\\"full\\" frame=\\"noframe\\" intro_animation=\\"none\\" full_width=\\"yes\\" lightbox=\\"no\\" link_target=\\"_self\\" width=\\"1/1\\" el_position=\\"first last\\"] [/spb_row] [spb_row parallax_video_height=\\"video-height\\" parallax_video_overlay=\\"none\\" parallax_image_height=\\"content-height\\" parallax_image_movement=\\"fixed\\" parallax_image_speed=\\"0.5\\" row_overlay_opacity=\\"0\\" width=\\"1/1\\" el_position=\\"first last\\"] [sitemap el_class=\\"sitemap1\\" width=\\"1/4\\" el_position=\\"first\\"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom=\\"no\\" pb_border_bottom=\\"no\\" width=\\"3/4\\" el_position=\\"last\\"] <p>The VIMMI CDN video delivery network is designed to quickly and reliably deliver flawless SD and HD Adaptive Bit Rate (ABR) video to any screen or device, worldwide, over unmanaged IP networks. It provides an exceptional customer experience by reducing the amount of traffic that must be transferred between the origin point and an ISP over what are usually low bandwidth links. VIMMI ensures high stream quality even when bandwidth is relatively low.</p><p>VIMMI enables operators and content owners to rapidly scale their CDN capacity to reach an unlimited number of viewers, everywhere, around the globe.</p><p>The CDN effortlessly handles all video formats and profiles. Its streaming servers offer exceptional traffic throughput and consumer connection support. Advanced distributed storage technology provides outstanding reliability and quality of service across any geographical span. As an open platform, all system elements use APIs to make setup and integration with the customer environment fast and simple.</p><p>VIMMI professionally-staffed NOC stands behind up its highly resilient, reliable CDN. The NOC is available to help at any time, day or night, every day of the year, 24x7x365.</p><ul><li><a href=\\"http://vimmi.loc/node/16\\">VIMMI Global Network</a></li><li><a href=\\"http://vimmi.loc/node/17\\">VIMMI Global Network Operations Center</a></li><li><a href=\\"http://vimmi.loc/node/18\\">CDN Management System</a></li><li><a href=\\"http://vimmi.loc/node/19\\">Live streaming</a></li><li><a href=\\"http://vimmi.loc/node/24\\">VOD streaming and personalization</a></li><li><a href=\\"http://vimmi.loc/node/30\\">Mobile Video Delivery</a></li><li><a href=\\"http://vimmi.loc/node/31\\">Analytics and reporting</a></li><li><a href=\\"http://vimmi.loc/node/32\\">Advanced, customizable video player for PCs</a></li></ul> [/spb_text_block] [/spb_row] ";}s:21:"back-office_219010298";a:2:{s:4:"name";s:11:"back office";s:8:"template";s:6952:"[spb_row wrap_type=\\"full-width\\" parallax_type=\\"color\\" bg_type=\\"cover\\" parallax_video_height=\\"video-height\\" parallax_video_overlay=\\"none\\" parallax_image_height=\\"content-height\\" parallax_image_movement=\\"fixed\\" parallax_image_speed=\\"0.5\\" row_overlay_opacity=\\"0\\" row_padding_vertical=\\"0\\" row_margin_vertical=\\"0\\" remove_element_spacing=\\"no\\" width=\\"1/1\\" el_position=\\"first last\\"] [spb_single_image image=\\"209\\" image_size=\\"full\\" frame=\\"noframe\\" intro_animation=\\"none\\" full_width=\\"yes\\" lightbox=\\"no\\" link_target=\\"_self\\" width=\\"1/1\\" el_position=\\"first last\\"] [/spb_row] [spb_row parallax_video_height=\\"video-height\\" parallax_video_overlay=\\"none\\" parallax_image_height=\\"content-height\\" parallax_image_moveme