reparation, delivery and monetization of video, while meeting today’s pricing pressures.<br>[/sf_iconbox][/one_fourth_last]</p> [/fullwidth_text] [blank_spacer height=\\"50px\\" width=\\"1/1\\" el_position=\\"first last\\"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom=\\"no\\" pb_border_bottom=\\"no\\" el_class=\\"back1\\" width=\\"1/3\\" el_position=\\"first\\"] <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\">Prepare</h3><p>We have assembled a comprehensive suite of Media Asset Management services in a single cloud-based user interface, enabling live and VOD multi-screen transcoding, metadata insertion, content protection...</p><p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">[sf_button colour=\\"accent\\" type=\\"sf-icon-reveal\\" size=\\"standard\\" link=\\"http://wordpress.vimmi.loc/?page_id=304\\" target=\\"_self\\" icon=\\"ss-pointright\\" dropshadow=\\"no\\" extraclass=\\"\\"] Learn More [/sf_button]</p> [/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom=\\"no\\" pb_border_bottom=\\"no\\" el_class=\\"back2\\" width=\\"1/3\\"] <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\">Monetize</h3><p>We have unified all vital monetization elements into a single Content Management System that includes: user management and CRM, billing, and EPG catalogue, and integrated them with our mobile applications ...</p><p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">[sf_button colour=\\"accent\\" type=\\"sf-icon-reveal\\" size=\\"standard\\" link=\\"http://wordpress.vimmi.loc/?page_id=436\\" target=\\"_self\\" icon=\\"ss-pointright\\" dropshadow=\\"no\\" extraclass=\\"\\"] Learn More [/sf_button]</p> [/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom=\\"no\\" pb_border_bottom=\\"no\\" el_class=\\"back3\\" width=\\"1/3\\" el_position=\\"last\\"] <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\">Stream</h3><p>Our ‘CDN in a box’ was designed on the basis that current network infrastructures are not sufficient to support the massive global online consumption of video, without compromising on video quality...</p><p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">[sf_button colo