(204, 1, '2015-12-23 12:46:27', '2015-12-23 12:46:27', 'Due to innovative machine learning architecture, We have built a better global network, one that is specially tuned for the rigorous demands of video delivery. The platform optimizes delays and network resources to provide unprecedented QoS (Quality of service). It uses a novel architecture that minimizes go-to-market and operational costs, along with ensuring fast deployment and effective scalability.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Designed for flexible granularity</h4>\r\nBy providing a distributed system of many PoPs with inherent self-management - not needing to compromise and be limited by deploying only few large server farms.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Designed for scalability</h4>\r\nEnabling highly-optimal inherent scalability, starting from a single server in a PoP, expanded seamlessly to a network of multiple servers in distributed PoPs, dynamically merged together, constantly, for having utmost efficiency and superb cost-performance, supporting customers throughout their growth cycles.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Designed for network usage optimization</h4>\r\nThe content bandwidth consumption is optimized, live, while preserving high QoS per content provider and end-user, considering, the type of content, its instant needs, and the overall profile of content consumption across the CDN and the internet at any given time, along the content consumption time.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Machine learning</h4>\r\nThrough pattern recognition for each content provider, Vimmi Media Delivery Platform algorithms learn and makes decisions of content upload and consumption and optimize content and resources allocation throughout the platform with the primary intention to reduce costs such as amount of service requests between edge and origin while improving the video quality and experience of end-users.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">''Media-Box'' granularity and cache sharing</h4>\r\nAll the functionalities can be arranged on multiple servers or having all of them in a single server, in a completely flexible and dynamic manner – Media-Box which includes, at the same server, several key capabilities such as origin, packaging, caching, streaming, management and service routing, working at a very high density.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Easy, rapid &amp; infinite scalability</h4>\r\nWithin few hours, servers functioning as a Media Box, and Edge or any other functionality of the platform, can be added and put into full live service, at practically any available PoP across the internet. Very high scalability is further supported by almost effortless definition of sub-groups and sub-platform clusters within large clusters of servers.\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">Smart Storage</h3>\r\nAs the sheer number of hours of owned content increases, storage capacity for video assets must keep pace—meaning more servers, more backup, more security, more real estate, more technical support—and more headaches and expenses. The flexible cloud-based asset storage solution scales with your business, so you pay only for the storage you need. Its advanced distributed storage technology achieves outstanding reliability and quality of service and reaches around the globe. Content can be served, at the speed of light, across the proprietary Vimmi platform for delivery right to user access networks. Assets are loaded once and can be instantly multiplied to other storage locations and on-demand across geographies, in accordance with established policy. Vimmi storage services provide professional-grade protection and backup to ensure the safety and security of your valuable video. With no single point of failure and virtually unlimited redundancy, Vimmi distributed storage satisfies your business’s need for ready access to high-quality video. It provides vast storage volumes for large content libraries of any digital asset, from media files to databases, at very low cost. Our Content Storage service scales with your needs, so get all the high-performance, high-availability storage capacity you need at each point in time without expending scarce resources on purchasing, managing or supporting infrastructure. The Vimmi distributed storage service is specially designed as versatile video storage infrastructure that can: [list] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Provide exceptionally reliable and advanced video distribution services [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Serve your current and future storage requirements through dynamic growth as your activities and project needs increase [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Serve content from the server that is closest to the customer [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Create copy at upload and ensure that two or more replications, per customer account policies, and backup copies exist for all content at any given moment [/list_item] [/list] <strong>Features:</strong> [list] [list_item icon="ss-check"] SLA for 100% availability [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Integration with pay-for-use billing covering storage, traffic, and transactions [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Logical directory structure [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Localized ingest and content access [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Ingest via FTP, sFTP, FTPs, RSYNC, SSH, and HTTP [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Support for applying conditional rules across objects and folders, such as age and MIME type [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Programmable API eases workflow automation and integration with customer-owned storage systems [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Enables post-upload transcoding [/list_item] [/list]', 'Global Media Delivery Platform', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'global-media-delivery-network', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:07:29', '2017-03-17 11:07:29', '', 0, 'http://vimmi.loc/?page_id=204', 0, 'page', '', 0),
