(213, 1, '2015-12-24 04:59:20', '2015-12-24 04:59:20', '[spb_row wrap_type="content-width" parallax_type="color" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="0" row_margin_vertical="0" remove_element_spacing="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [/spb_row] [boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n\r\nFor our commercial and white label CDN customers, Vimmi provides a NOC staffed with video OTT and CDN professionals who are available and eager to help, 24x7x365. ISPs and video service providers that offer Vimmi CDN services on a white label basis may choose to use our NOC services or license Vimmi NOC tools so they can support video CDN services via their own operations center.\r\n\r\nSophisticated Vimmi NOC tools reduce operational expense with highly integrated and automated monitoring and alerting tools that can be successfully operated by a small staff. Intuitive interfaces present a clear overview of important status information and provide easy access to additional mission-critical data.\r\n\r\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]', 'Network Operating Center (NOC)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'vimmi-noc', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:22:43', '2017-03-17 11:22:43', '', 0, 'http://vimmi.loc/?page_id=213', 0, 'page', '', 0),
