(278, 1, '2015-12-24 09:53:18', '2015-12-24 09:53:18', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n\r\nMore than ever before, viewers today expect a seamless, cross-platform viewing experience when they are on the move. On smart phones, tablets and other devices, they want high quality playback.\r\n\r\nVimmi automatically associates the appropriate format with each requesting device and delivers the transcoded video that matches its distinct video requirements.\r\n[list]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Delivers video to any platform and device [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Supports mobile apps and sites [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Open APIs make integration a snap [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Provides ideal transcoding for mobile devices [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Automatically detects smart devices [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Compatible with HTML 5 [/list_item]\r\n[/list]\r\n\r\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]', 'Mobile Video Delivery', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mobile-video-delivery', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:20:50', '2017-03-17 11:20:50', '', 0, 'http://vimmi.loc/?page_id=278', 0, 'page', '', 0),
