(300, 3, '2015-12-24 10:58:12', '2015-12-24 10:58:12', '[spb_row parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="1264" image_size="medium" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="no" lightbox="yes" link_target="_self" width="1/4" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="3/4" el_position="last"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">WHITE LABEL VIDEO CDN</h3>\r\nFor service providers that prefer to outsource video CDN service operations—but still want to offer those services under their own brand--VIMMI is pleased to provide comprehensive white label CDN services. Under the white-label program, VIMMI owns and operates the CDN for the service provider on our own hardware platform and all services are provided under the service provider’s brand.\r\n\r\nFirst level support is provided by the ISP or video service provider, but VIMMI handles more complex service issues. VIMMI also offers optional assistance with sales, system engineering and structuring the video CDN business.\r\n\r\n<strong>Advantages of VIMMI white label video CDN</strong>\r\n\r\nVIMMI video CDN is the best white label service for delivering video over managed and unmanaged networks. As specialists in video CDN, VIMMI has an impressive track record of success. Our hard-earned expertise translates into higher QoS, greater control of your network and more opportunities to monetize network resources.\r\n\r\nVIMMI assists its white label clients in acquiring the skill set needed to promote CDNs through business rules, pricing and business engineering.\r\n\r\nVIMMI white label CDN users benefit from:\r\n[list]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Offering profitable and relevant new services to existing clients [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Designed-for-video CDN platform [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Proven best-of-breed technology that delivers high QoS [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] 24x7x365 NOC [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Real time analytics and reporting [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Fastest time-to-market [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Support for emerging standards, formats and viewing platforms [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] LowOPEX [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Expert guidance in building a strong, viable content delivery business [/list_item]\r\n[/list]\r\n\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]', 'WHITE LABEL VIDEO CDN', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '300-2', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:40:41', '2017-03-17 11:40:41', '', 0, 'http://vimmi.loc/?page_id=300', 0, 'page', '', 0),
