(447, 1, '2015-12-27 08:32:47', '2015-12-27 08:32:47', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n\r\nVimmi CMS creates a collaborative platform that enables you to edit, publish and modify content and to add your own touch to existing content. Manage all content from a central location without any need for special infrastructure or equipment other than a PC. Easy-to-use backoffice tools enable bulk uploading of content and make it simple to manage the catalog. Templates speed implementation of web and iOS/Android tablet front ends, and flexible widgets and APIs allow content to be embedded in social media and customer web sites.\r\n\r\nVimmi CMS helps you effectively promote and market video assets to existing and potential customers. Maximize penetration, market share, revenues and ARPU by personalizing content for each viewer and adapting it as needed for each social networking site by managing and controlling content offers, purchases and ad campaigns.\r\n\r\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]', 'Content Management System (CMS)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'content-management-system-cms', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:00:34', '2017-03-17 11:00:34', '', 0, 'http://vimmi.loc/?page_id=447', 0, 'page', '', 0),
