(460, 1, '2015-12-27 09:11:53', '2015-12-27 09:11:53', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n\r\nMedia asset management, which handles assets to be delivered on demand and via playlists to a range of target devices, is an essential element of a complete OTT system. It includes\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[list]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Asset administration [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Classification [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Publisher information [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Asset packaging [/list_item]\r\n[/list]\r\nA recommendations engine based on artificial intelligence generates valuable statistics and viewing data and provides customers with recommendations in keeping with their individual preferences. It compiles small changes in individual preferences to identify emerging trends. Because analysis is based on iterative learning, it becomes increasingly accurate over time.\r\n\r\nAn EPG serves as the user interface with the asset management system. In order to enable its customers to efficiently and accurately create EPGs, EPG tools automatically connect to ingest systems and import XMLTV-formatted EPG data via a dedicated application. Time conflicts are automatically resolved by the system, when possible. When they cannot be resolved automatically, the system notifies an administrator about the conflict. Operation can be scheduled to enable EPG data to be imported at a time, from each possible source. The data may be manually edited to add or remove shows or alter their parameters.\r\n\r\nThe VIMMI program planning and scheduling service is easy to learn and easy to use, even for novice WebTV administrators. It is ideal for linear or playout channels. The service provides accurate calendar views, syncing with playout or OTT systems/servers in real time and integration with the asset management system. For any time slot, the scheduler can program secondary graphic events and it maintains a comprehensive run log to track concurrence between planning and performance.\r\n\r\n<strong>EPG Tools</strong>\r\n[list]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Ingest connectors. Import the EPG from the widely-used XMLTV format via dedicated application. [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Scheduled automatization. Automatically import the EPG data anytime you like, from any number of possible sources. [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Manual editing. If necessary, you can use the EPG console to add and remove shows, as well as edit their parameters. [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Conflict resolver. The system is equipped with an automatic detector of conflicting time show information, resolving them itself when possible, or notifying the EPG administrator when in doubt. [/list_item]\r\n[/list]\r\n<strong>TV Scheduler (*)</strong>\r\n\r\nTV Scheduler is the entry level program planning and scheduling tool, perfectly fits the need for the new startup webTV linear channels (info, movies, cartoons, news channels, etc..) or playout channels.\r\n[list]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Frame accurate calendar view [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Playout system or OTT video server realtime sync [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] EPG connector (XML TV web service) [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Asset management integration [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Ingest list [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Secondary graphics events [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] As-Run-Log [/list_item]\r\n[/list]\r\n\r\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]</script>', 'Media Asset Management', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'media-asset-management', '', '', '2017-02-15 20:57:31', '2017-02-15 20:57:31', '', 0, 'http://vimmi.loc/?page_id=460', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(464, 1, '2015-12-27 09:23:22', '2015-12-27 09:23:22', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Campaign and Affiliate Management</h4>\r\nFor affiliate marketing, the Vimmi Monetization Suite provides a complete cloud-based platform for cross-promotion, cross-selling and revenue sharing. The affiliate marketing module provides sophisticated tools for creating and refining highly effective integrated campaigns and packages and for allocating revenues to affiliate program partners.\r\n\r\nCreate a range of viewing destinations to generate greatest returns on your content\r\nPublish videos to more websites by invisibly overlaying the Vimmi player on a partner or affiliate''s player\r\nControl your content with management tools including a variety of account authorizations\r\nPowerful analytics integrated in Vimmi embedded players provide viewer response data even when content is viewed on affiliate sites\r\nBoost content sales by enabling viewers to purchase content via the Vimmi content player that is embedded on partner and affiliate websites.\r\n\r\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]', 'Campain & Affiliate Mamagement', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'campaign-affiliate-management', '', '', '2017-03-17 10:52:15', '2017-03-17 10:52:15', '', 0, 'http://vimmi.loc/?page_id=464', 0, 'page', '', 0),
