(569, 1, '2017-03-17 11:41:09', '2017-03-17 11:41:09', '[spb_row wrap_type="full-width" parallax_type="color" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="30" row_margin_vertical="30" remove_element_spacing="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="1260" image_size="full" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="yes" lightbox="no" link_target="_self" width="1/3" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="2/3" el_position="last"]\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">VIMMI, the technology leader in distributed video delivery network platforms, has designed a suite of video services that empower content owners and operators to fully monetize their video assets. These services include the VIMMI global video Content Delivery Network (CDN), in-cloud content preparation services, a modular in-cloud <em>Back Office &amp; Video Monetization Suite</em> and a ready-to-use <em>OTT-as-a-service</em> solution.</p>\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">For ISP’s and Telecom operators we are pleased to provide <em>white label global video CDN</em>. So now you can run your business and focus on marketing and maximizing your profits while VIMMI manages CDN services for you and assumes full responsibility for all infrastructure and operations. If at any time you wish to switch to your own CDN platform, VIMMI will gladly license the system to you to ensure a seamless transition.</p>\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">The global CDN service is based on a technology platform designed and developed by VIMMI. VIMMI is committed to creating advanced solutions that efficiently address the challenges of equipping networks for the future.</p>\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row] [spb_row wrap_type="full-width" row_bg_color="#eaf4f6" parallax_type="color" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="30" row_margin_vertical="30" remove_element_spacing="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="1260" image_size="full" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="yes" lightbox="no" link_target="_self" width="1/3" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="2/3" el_position="last"]\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">VIMMI was founded by visionaries who foresaw the multi-platform, anywhere, anytime video future and were committed to making that future easily accessible to any content owner, service provider, enterprise or public organization.</p>\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">VIMMI is realizing its mission with innovative, <em><strong>comprehensive</strong></em> built-for-video network architecture technologies that provide cloud-based video services and broadcast-quality delivery services across managed and unmanaged networks. VIMMI enables its customers to reach any screen, at any time, with any content from any location in the world and to maximize return on their valuable video assets.</p>\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">As pioneers in video and IP integration, the company’s founders and leaders are natives in a technology landscape where many players from the video and IP worlds are still learning the basic terrain. The VIMMI solution reflects their experience and expertise.</p>\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">Since 2009, the VIMMI platform has provided a full suite of cloud-based, modular service provider-grade video preparation, delivery and management services. An open platform that is integrated via APIs, it is uniquely fast and easy to set up, freeing clients from the complex, costly and delay-prone process of building in-house video processing systems.</p>\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">VIMMI also provides robust, turnkey white label CDN services for video and internet service providers, enabling them to rapidly add advanced OTT delivery to their service offerings without burdensome investments in infrastructure and manpower.</p>\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]<script>', 'WHY VIMMI?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '492-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:41:09', '2017-03-17 11:41:09', '', 492, 'http://vimmi.loc/?p=569', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
