(1330, 1, '2017-03-17 11:29:06', '2017-03-17 11:29:06', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Subscriber Management System (SMS)</h4>\nVimmi offers powerful web based subscribers management solution to maintain subscribers, products or packages, contracts, billing, revenues, inventory and provisioning. The Subscriber Management System could contain customer relevant information and be responsible for keeping track of placed orders, credit limits, invoicing and payments, as well as generation of reports and statistics.\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Customer Relationship Management (CRM)</h4>\nReal time, hands-on customer relationship management is key to maximizing ARPU as well as growing the user base. The Vimmi CRM module enables content owners and operators to actively monitor, log, analyze and segment customer activity and purchase triggers. Based on this information, content, delivery platforms and pricing models can be customized to address the unique preferences of each customer segment.\n\nCloud-based customer support tools provide operator service reps with clear subscriber history and analysis that transforms every service call into an opportunity to increase customer usage and revenues while managing customer needs.\n\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]<s', 'Subscriber Management System & CRM', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '470-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:29:06', '2017-03-17 11:29:06', '', 470, 'http://vimmi.loc/?p=1330', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1352, 1, '2017-03-17 11:40:33', '2017-03-17 11:40:33', '[spb_row parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="1264" image_size="medium" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="no" lightbox="yes" link_target="_self" width="1/4" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="3/4" el_position="last"]\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">WHITE LABEL VIDEO CDN</h3>\nFor service providers that prefer to outsource video CDN service operations—but still want to offer those services under their own brand--VIMMI is pleased to provide comprehensive white label CDN services. Under the white-label program, VIMMI owns and operates the CDN for the service provider on our own hardware platform and all services are provided under the service provider’s brand.\n\nFirst level support is provided by the ISP or video service provider, but VIMMI handles more complex service issues. VIMMI also offers optional assistance with sales, system engineering and structuring the video CDN business.\n\n<strong>Advantages of VIMMI white label video CDN</strong>\n\nVIMMI video CDN is the best white label service for delivering video over managed and unmanaged networks. As specialists in video CDN, VIMMI has an impressive track record of success. Our hard-earned expertise translates into higher QoS, greater control of your network and more opportunities to monetize network resources.\n\nVIMMI assists its white label clients in acquiring the skill set needed to promote CDNs through business rules, pricing and business engineering.\n\nVIMMI white label CDN users benefit from:\n[list]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Offering profitable and relevant new services to existing clients [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Designed-for-video CDN platform [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Proven best-of-breed technology that delivers high QoS [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] 24x7x365 NOC [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Real time analytics and reporting [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Fastest time-to-market [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Support for emerging standards, formats and viewing platforms [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] LowOPEX [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Expert guidance in building a strong, viable content delivery business [/list_item]\n[/list]\n\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]', 'WHITE LABEL VIDEO CDN', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '300-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:40:33', '2017-03-17 11:40:33', '', 300, 'http://vimmi.loc/?p=1352', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1371, 1, '2017-03-03 12:17:20', '2017-03-03 12:17:20', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\nVimmi empowers content <a href="https://edit-my-paper.net/grade-my-paper/" style="text-decoration: none; color:#333;">grade-my-paper/</a> owners and broadcasters to generate returns on online videos with a menu of advertising approaches that increase ad spend. Customers may choose to partner with third-party ad-server networks or proprietary ad servers and to offer rich media, video and display ads to maximize ad spend. Additional ad options include contextual, linear and non-linear ads, contextual ads and ads that are placed within the video content.\n\nFor every video asset, ad decision engines maximize revenues by integrating with the Vimmi ad decision engine as well as ad-server network partners.\n\nThe Vimmi solution offers content owners the ability to maintain full control over advertising campaigns at both the video and channel level. It also allows owners to create targeting options, implement ad insertion policies, and adjust channel frequencies.\n\n<strong>Features:</strong>\n[list]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Flexible online ad insertion tools  [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Support for a multiple ad formats, servers, and networks [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Targeting by individual video file and video channel [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Access to proprietary ad server [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Fully integrate with third-party ad servers and networks, such as Adaptv, AdTech, Tremor Media, and more [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Policy-based ad insertion [/list_item]\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Support for linear, non-linear, contextual, and in-video ads [/list_item]\n[/list]\n\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]</script>', 'Ad Insertion', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '424-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-03-03 12:17:20', '2017-03-03 12:17:20', '', 424, 'http://vimmi.loc/?p=1371', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
