(1769, 1, '2015-12-23 10:57:18', '2015-12-23 10:57:18', 'Over 25 years of innovation leadership. Experience: Innovative Solutions Specialist - ImageSat International, Director for R&amp;D – Hi-Park, VP Projects &amp; Development – Market Square IP, VP Mobile Solutions – Catch Media inc., CTO – Zlango, Director for customers solutions – Mobixell Networks, CTO – Vimatix.\r\n• Expert in developing and implementing Multi-disciplinary systems and Cloud based mobile &amp; web solutions and applications.\r\n• Utilizing vast and diverse experience to significantly shorten learning curves and thus development costs.\r\n• Identifying and overcoming the major technology barriers, and mentoring the solutions and system engineering; IP research and patents promotion.\r\n• Linking technology and business aspects to market related requirements.\r\n• Managing companies IP and maintaining patents portfolios.\r\n• Strategic consulting to entrepreneurs, CEO’s, and cooperates decisions makers.\r\n• Main/Co-inventor in over 10 registered patents.\r\n• Actively participated in MPEG, 3GPP and OMA world’s standard comities.\r\nEducation:\r\nTel Aviv University: BA Economics, BSc Electronics &amp; Electrical Engineering.\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=AAkAAACgaooBUMk5pOGb_XwyJzUIbQTCWcO694Y&amp;authType=NAME_SEARCH&amp;authToken=Evth&amp;locale=en_US&amp;trk=tyah&amp;trkInfo=clickedVertical%3Amynetwork%2CclickedEntityId%3A10513034%2CauthType%3ANAME_SEARCH%2Cidx%3A1-6-6%2CtarId%3A1451303905820%2Ctas%3Aehud%20">LinkedIn Profile</a>', 'Ehud Spiegel', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ehud-spiegel', '', '', '2015-12-28 15:17:30', '2015-12-28 15:17:30', '', 0, 'http://vimmi.loc/?post_type=team&#038;p=1769', 0, 'team', '', 0),
