(1775, 1, '2015-12-23 11:09:19', '2015-12-23 11:09:19', 'Founded and managed several successful high-tech companies including:\r\nAtlantium - an infrastructure company in the water sector, main technology - a bacterial water purifier. As the CEO I led the founding team to define the company’s technological focus (UV water purification), CEO of\r\nVimatix - a leader in the development of platforms for creating and transferring multimedia to cellular. Amnon was hired by the seed investors to run the company. Achievements include raising $10M in three rounds of funding from US and Israeli VC''s., multimedia messaging solution for cellular,\r\nCOO of Electric Fuel - Electric Fuel developed battery-based energy systems for electric cars and employed 300 people. Amnon joined the core management team as the company’s Executive Vice President, responsible to implement the strategy of the company to become a global and leading company in its field.\r\nTook major and influencing part in the road-show with investment banking for IPO by the company in the NASDAQ (the company raised $100M). Established the operations of 200 employees located in Europe and US, and with the management team formed strategic partnerships with GM, Opel, Mercedes and the German postal authority.\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=AAkAABM2RkEBVpaFH5qiMwL-RCu7vkeVrviBSyE&amp;authType=NAME_SEARCH&amp;authToken=Gc0F&amp;locale=en_US&amp;trk=tyah&amp;trkInfo=clickedVertical%3Amynetwork%2CclickedEntityId%3A322324033%2CauthType%3ANAME_SEARCH%2Cidx%3A1-1-1%2CtarId%3A1451302976764%2Ctas%3Aamnon%20">LinkedIn Profile</a>', 'Amnon Sherf', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'amnon-sherf', '', '', '2015-12-28 15:05:27', '2015-12-28 15:05:27', '', 0, 'http://vimmi.loc/?post_type=team&#038;p=1775', 0, 'team', '', 0),
