(3971, 1, '2017-02-15 20:58:18', '2017-02-15 20:58:18', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n\r\nThe Vimmi video store enables you to quickly create a branded, cross-device, full-service solution for merchandising and delivering video offerings online, with support for delivery options including VOD, live channels, playlists, bundles, packages and more. The Video Store includes all tools that operators and content owners need to create a customized Internet store or application from scratch or to add a video store to an existing application or site.\r\n\r\nSales options such as VOD, live channels, playlists and linear channels enable you to deliver real value and drive revenues. With the Video Store, content owners can quickly create storefronts that provide a comprehensive solution for presenting, managing, delivering and billing for content. For clients who prefer to outsource store customization, Vimmi also provides customization assistance services.\r\n\r\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]<script>', 'Video Applications and Players', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '443-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-15 20:58:18', '2017-02-15 20:58:18', '', 443, 'http://vimmi.loc/443-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3972, 1, '2017-02-15 20:58:20', '2017-02-15 20:58:20', '[spb_row parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="199" image_size="medium" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="no" lightbox="yes" link_target="_self" width="1/4" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="3/4" el_position="last"]\r\n\r\n[dropcap1]A[/dropcap1]t VIMMI, we’ve built a better network—one that is specially tuned for the rigorous demands of video delivery.Our content delivery network (CDN) is designed for the millions of users who demand a high-quality video experience. Other CDNs install very small servers at thousands of locations, a technique that worked when most users surfed among small HTML files over poor connections.\r\n\r\nToday, both the supply of content and demand for it have exploded. So we’ve developed new methodology that is ideal for the new world of high-speed connections and rich video content. We’ve selected a smaller number of strategic global locations among the primary Internet Exchange Points, and built supercharged points of presence we call VIMMI GigaPOPs. These GigaPOPs have massive numbers of 10Gbps throughput servers and are directly connected to all major backbone networks.\r\n\r\nThe VIMMI network features unique architecture as well as global reach that is based on direct optical fiber connections to over 1,200 ISPs worldwide. It supports a full in-cloud solution for flat-fee OTT as well as an easy-to-operate fee-for-service model. The VIMMI platform provides 99.9999% network availability at extremely low set-up costs and with virtually no capital investment. Just choose the system elements that you need to complete your solution and VIMMI will provide them on a full-managed service basis.is text.\r\n\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]<script>', 'VIMMI GLOBAL NETWORK', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '230-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-15 20:58:20', '2017-02-15 20:58:20', '', 230, 'http://vimmi.loc/230-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3973, 1, '2017-02-15 20:58:21', '2017-02-15 20:58:21', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">VOD Streaming</h3>\r\nUpsell your valuable video assets with efficient, personalized and cost-effective VOD streaming services. Using the Vimmi Media Delivery Platform, you can stream personalized content to viewers from cloud-based Vimmi video storage and caching servers. Scalable and distributed broadcast-grade platform architecture grows with your business and with asset volume, so you pay only for what you need, when you need it—and never get caught short if demand suddenly spikes.\r\n\r\nVimmi VOD services integrate easily with leading subscriber billing and management systems to support pay-per-view, ad-supported and subscription based VOD consumption across multiple devices and screens.\r\n\r\nSocial tools can be integrated to enhance user interactivity and grow both the subscriber base and usage among existing subscribers.\r\n\r\nVIMMI cloud-based transcoding-as-a-service creates file-based assets for adaptive streaming. Save on transcoding expenses, free up storage space and make it easier and less costly to manage video assets by streaming HDS, HLS, HSS, DASH and RTSP.\r\n\r\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]<script>', 'VOD Streaming', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '252-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-15 20:58:21', '2017-02-15 20:58:21', '', 252, 'http://vimmi.loc/252-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
