(4208, 1, '2017-03-17 10:20:55', '2017-03-17 10:20:55', '[spb_row wrap_type="content-width" row_bg_color="#ffffff" parallax_type="color" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="30" row_margin_vertical="0" remove_element_spacing="yes" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="1730" image_size="medium" frame="noframe" intro_animation="spin" full_width="yes" lightbox="no" link_target="_self" width="1/3" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block title="About VIMMI" pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="2/3" el_position="last"]\r\n\r\nVimmi was founded by visionaries <a style="text-decoration: none; color: #333;" href="https://edit-my-paper.net/grade-my-paper/">grade-my-paper/</a> who foresaw the multi-platform, anywhere, anytime video future and were committed to making that future easily accessible <a style="text-decoration: none; color: #333;" href="https://essaywritingservicehelp.co.uk/proofreading/">proofreading</a> to any content owner, service provider, enterprise or public organization.\r\n\r\nVimmi is realizing its mission with innovative, comprehensive built-for-video network architecture technologies that provide cloud-based video services and broadcast-quality delivery services across managed and unmanaged networks. Vimmi enables its customers to reach any screen, at any time, with any content from any location in the world and to maximize return on their valuable video assets.\r\n\r\nAs pioneers in video and IP integration, the company’s founders and leaders are natives in a technology landscape where many players from the video and IP worlds are still learning the basic terrain. The Vimmi solution reflects their experience and expertise.\r\n\r\nSince 2011, the Vimmi platform has provided a full suite of cloud-based, modular service provider-grade video preparation, delivery and management services. An open platform that is integrated via APIs, it is uniquely fast and easy to set up, freeing clients from the complex, costly and delay-prone process of building in-house video processing systems.\r\n\r\nVimmi also provides robust, Licensed CDN services for video and internet service providers, enabling them to rapidly add advanced OTT delivery to their service offerings without burdensome investments in infrastructure and manpower.\r\n\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row] [spb_row wrap_type="content-width" row_bg_color="#2eafba" parallax_type="color" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="30" row_margin_vertical="0" remove_element_spacing="yes" row_el_class="fontswhite" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_tabs tab_asset_title="Why VIMMI?" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_tab title="" id=""] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n\r\nVIMMI, the technology leader in distributed video delivery network platforms, has designed a suite of video services that empower content owners and operators to fully monetize their video assets. These services include the VIMMI global video Content Delivery Network (CDN), in-cloud content preparation services, a modular in-cloud Back Office &amp; Video Monetization Suite and a ready-to-use OTT-as-a-service solution.\r\n\r\nFor ISP’s and Telecom operators we are pleased to provide white label global video CDN. So now you can run your business and focus on marketing and maximizing your profits while VIMMI manages CDN services for you and assumes full responsibility for all infrastructure and operations. If at any time you wish to switch to your own CDN platform, VIMMI will gladly license the system to you to ensure a seamless transition.\r\n\r\nThe global CDN service is based on a technology platform designed and developed by VIMMI. VIMMI is committed to creating advanced solutions that efficiently address the challenges of equipping networks for the future.\r\n\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_tab] [spb_tab title="" id=""] [/spb_tab] [spb_tab title="" id=""] [/spb_tab] [spb_tab title="" id=""] [/spb_tab] [/spb_tabs] [/spb_row] [spb_row wrap_type="content-width" row_bg_color="#ffffff" parallax_type="color" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="window-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="30" row_margin_vertical="0" remove_element_spacing="yes" row_el_class="mb0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">We are Vimmi</h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">This is our dedicated team who work day-in and day-out together to\r\nbring our clients the most amazing projects for a digitally connected world.</p>\r\n[hr]\r\n\r\n[/spb_text_block] [team_carousel category="All" excerpt_length="16" profile_link="yes" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [/spb_row] [testimonial_slider title="What our clients say about us" text_size="large" item_count="6" order="rand" category="All" autoplay="yes" alt_background="alt-four" el_class="mt0 bt0 no-arrow mb0 testimonial_content" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_row wrap_type="content-width" row_bg_color="#ffffff" parallax_type="color" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="content-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="30" row_margin_vertical="0" remove_element_spacing="yes" row_el_class="customersection" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [b