(4219, 1, '2017-03-17 10:59:08', '2017-03-17 10:59:08', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n\r\nVimmi supports creation of in-cloud 24-hour linear content loops that can be played out via OTT, mobile streaming and Web TV channels. The linear playout channel server schedules on-demand video assets or combines video assets with live event streams. Linear channels may be monetized through the insertion of channel-related advertising or any other subscription alternatives.\r\n\r\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]', 'Cloud Playout', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '1932-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 10:59:08', '2017-03-17 10:59:08', '', 1932, 'http://vimmi.loc/1932-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4220, 1, '2017-03-17 11:00:34', '2017-03-17 11:00:34', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n\r\nVimmi CMS creates a collaborative platform that enables you to edit, publish and modify content and to add your own touch to existing content. Manage all content from a central location without any need for special infrastructure or equipment other than a PC. Easy-to-use backoffice tools enable bulk uploading of content and make it simple to manage the catalog. Templates speed implementation of web and iOS/Android tablet front ends, and flexible widgets and APIs allow content to be embedded in social media and customer web sites.\r\n\r\nVimmi CMS helps you effectively promote and market video assets to existing and potential customers. Maximize penetration, market share, revenues and ARPU by personalizing content for each viewer and adapting it as needed for each social networking site by managing and controlling content offers, purchases and ad campaigns.\r\n\r\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]', 'Content Management System (CMS)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '447-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:00:34', '2017-03-17 11:00:34', '', 447, 'http://vimmi.loc/447-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4221, 1, '2017-03-17 11:01:53', '2017-03-17 11:01:53', '[spb_row parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<h3><a href="http://vimmi.loc/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/inner_page_monetization.png"><img class=" size-full wp-image-458 aligncenter" src="http://vimmi.loc/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/inner_page_monetization.png" alt="inner_page_monetization" width="924" height="178" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3>CONTENT PREPARATION</h3>\r\nTranscode, store and protect your content on any viewing device using the most advanced Adaptive Bit Rate (ABR) encoders and wrappers.\r\n\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]', 'CONTENT PREPARATION', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '474-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:01:53', '2017-03-17 11:01:53', '', 474, 'http://vimmi.loc/474-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4222, 1, '2017-03-17 11:04:04', '2017-03-17 11:04:04', '[spb_row parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="1261" image_size="medium" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="no" lightbox="yes" link_target="_self" width="1/4" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="3/4" el_position="last"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">DELIVER A SUPERIOR ON-DEMAND EXPERIENCE</h3>\r\nDeliver instant on-demand playback with pause, rewind and seek capabilities. Customize viewing experiences by specifying time-offset and duration to play a video from any starting point without editing.\r\n\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]', 'DELIVER A SUPERIOR ON-DEMAND', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '266-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:04:04', '2017-03-17 11:04:04', '', 266, 'http://vimmi.loc/266-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4223, 1, '2017-03-17 11:05:02', '2017-03-17 11:05:02', '[spb_row parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="1260" image_size="medium" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="no" lightbox="yes" link_target="_self" width="1/4" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="3/4" el_position="last"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">DELIVER H.264 VIDEO ON-DEMAND TO YOUR CUSTOMERS, WHEREVER THEY ARE</h3>\r\nTreat your customers to the high video quality they value, regardless of where they are and what viewing platform the use. VIMMI enables you to simultaneously deliver high-quality pre-recorded video and audio streams to any player and any device, using any protocol.\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]', 'DELIVER H.264 VIDEO', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '257-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:05:02', '2017-03-17 11:05:02', '', 257, 'http://vimmi.loc/257-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4224, 1, '2017-03-17 11:06:05', '2017-03-17 11:06:05', '[spb_row parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="199" image_size="medium" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="no" lightbox="yes" link_target="_self" width="1/4" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="3/4" el_position="last"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">Distributed storage</h3>\r\nAs the sheer number of hours of owned content increases, storage capacity for video assets must keep pace—meaning more servers, more backup, more security, more real estate, more technical support—and more headaches and expenses.\r\n\r\nThe flexible VIMMI cloud-based asset storage solution scales with your business, so you pay only for the storage you need. Its advanced distributed storage technology achieves outstanding reliability and quality of service and reaches around the globe. Content can be served, at the speed of light, across the proprietary VIMMI platform for delivery right to user access networks. Assets are loaded once and can be instantly multiplied to other VIMMI storage locations and on-demand across geographies, in accordance with established policy.\r\n\r\nVIMMI hosting services provide professional-grade protection and backup to ensure the safety and security of your valuable video. With no single point of failure and virtually unlimited redundancy, VIMMI distributed storage satisfies your business’s need for ready access to high-quality video. It provides vast storage volumes for large content libraries of any digital asset, from media files to databases, at very low cost.\r\n\r\nOur Content Storage service scales with your needs, so get all the high-performance, high-availability storage capacity you need at each point in time without expending scarce resources on purchasing, managing or supporting infrastructure.\r\n\r\nThe VIMMI distributed storage service is specially designed as versatile video storage infrastructure that can:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Provide exceptionally reliable and advanced video distribution services</li>\r\n	<li>Serve your current and future storage requirements through dynamic growth as your activities and project needs increase</li>\r\n	<li>Serve content from the server that is closest to the customer</li>\r\n	<li>Create copy at upload and ensure that two or more replications, per customer account policies, and backup copies exist for all content at any given moment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFeatures:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SLA for 100% availability</li>\r\n	<li>Integration with pay-for-use billing covering storage, traffic, and transactions</li>\r\n	<li>Logical directory structure</li>\r\n	<li>Localized ingest and content access</li>\r\n	<li>Ingest via FTP, sFTP, FTPs, RSYNC, SSH, and HTTP</li>\r\n	<li>Support for applying conditional rules across objects and folders, such as age and MIME type</li>\r\n	<li>Programmable API eases workflow automation and integration with customer-owned storage systems</li>\r\n	<li>Enables post-upload transcoding</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]', 'Distributed storage', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '420-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:06:05', '2017-03-17 11:06:05', '', 420, 'http://vimmi.loc/420-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4225, 1, '2017-03-17 11:07:29', '2017-03-17 11:07:29', 'Due to innovative machine learning architecture, We have built a better global network, one that is specially tuned for the rigorous demands of video delivery. The platform optimizes delays and network resources to provide unprecedented QoS (Quality of service). It uses a novel architecture that minimizes go-to-market and operational costs, along with ensuring fast deployment and effective scalability.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Designed for flexible granularity</h4>\r\nBy providing a distributed system of many PoPs with inherent self-management - not needing to compromise and be limited by deploying only few large server farms.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Designed for scalability</h4>\r\nEnabling highly-optimal inherent scalability, starting from a single server in a PoP, expanded seamlessly to a network of multiple servers in distributed PoPs, dynamically merged together, constantly, for having utmost efficiency and superb cost-performance, supporting customers throughout their growth cycles.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Designed for network usage optimization</h4>\r\nThe content bandwidth consumption is optimized, live, while preserving high QoS per content provider and end-user, considering, the type of content, its instant needs, and the overall profile of content consumption across the CDN and the internet at any given time, along the content consumption time.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Machine learning</h4>\r\nThrough pattern recognition for each content provider, Vimmi Media Delivery Platform algorithms learn and makes decisions of content upload and consumption and optimize content and resources allocation throughout the platform with the primary intention to reduce costs such as amount of service requests between edge and origin while improving the video quality and experience of end-users.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">''Media-Box'' granularity and cache sharing</h4>\r\nAll the functionalities can be arranged on multiple servers or having all of them in a single server, in a completely flexible and dynamic manner – Media-Box which includes, at the same server, several key capabilities such as origin, packaging, caching, streaming, management and service routing, working at a very high density.\r\n<h4 class="spb-heading">Easy, rapid &amp; infinite scalability</h4>\r\nWithin few hours, servers functioning as a Media Box, and Edge or any other functionality of the platform, can be added and put into full live service, at practically any available PoP across the internet. Very high scalability is further supported by almost effortless definition of sub-groups and sub-platform clusters within large clusters of servers.\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">Smart Storage</h3>\r\nAs the sheer number of hours of owned content increases, storage capacity for video assets must keep pace—meaning more servers, more backup, more security, more real estate, more technical support—and more headaches and expenses. The flexible cloud-based asset storage solution scales with your business, so you pay only for the storage you need. Its advanced distributed storage technology achieves outstanding reliability and quality of service and reaches around the globe. Content can be served, at the speed of light, across the proprietary Vimmi platform for delivery right to user access networks. Assets are loaded once and can be instantly multiplied to other storage locations and on-demand across geographies, in accordance with established policy. Vimmi storage services provide professional-grade protection and backup to ensure the safety and security of your valuable video. With no single point of failure and virtually unlimited redundancy, Vimmi distributed storage satisfies your business’s need for ready access to high-quality video. It provides vast storage volumes for large content libraries of any digital asset, from media files to databases, at very low cost. Our Content Storage service scales with your needs, so get all the high-performance, high-availability storage capacity you need at each point in time without expending scarce resources on purchasing, managing or supporting infrastructure. The Vimmi distributed storage service is specially designed as versatile video storage infrastructure that can: [list] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Provide exceptionally reliable and advanced video distribution services [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Serve your current and future storage requirements through dynamic growth as your activities and project needs increase [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Serve content from the server that is closest to the customer [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Create copy at upload and ensure that two or more replications, per customer account policies, and backup copies exist for all content at any given moment [/list_item] [/list] <strong>Features:</strong> [list] [list_item icon="ss-check"] SLA for 100% availability [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Integration with pay-for-use billing covering storage, traffic, and transactions [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Logical directory structure [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Localized ingest and content access [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Ingest via FTP, sFTP, FTPs, RSYNC, SSH, and HTTP [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Support for applying conditional rules across objects and folders, such as age and MIME type [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Programmable API eases workflow automation and integration with customer-owned storage systems [/list_item] [list_item icon="ss-check"] Enables post-upload transcoding [/list_item] [/list]', 'Global Media Delivery Platform', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '204-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:07:29', '2017-03-17 11:07:29', '', 204, 'http://vimmi.loc/204-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
