(4241, 1, '2017-03-17 11:33:51', '2017-03-17 11:33:51', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n\r\nThe Vimmi video store enables you to quickly create a branded, cross-device, full-service solution for merchandising and delivering video offerings online, with support for delivery options including VOD, live channels, playlists, bundles, packages and more. The Video Store includes all tools that operators and content owners need to create a customized Internet store or application from scratch or to add a video store to an existing application or site.\r\n\r\nSales options such as VOD, live channels, playlists and linear channels enable you to deliver real value and drive revenues. With the Video Store, content owners can quickly create storefronts that provide a comprehensive solution for presenting, managing, delivering and billing for content. For clients who prefer to outsource store customization, Vimmi also provides customization assistance services.\r\n\r\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]', 'Video Applications and Players', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '443-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:33:51', '2017-03-17 11:33:51', '', 443, 'http://vimmi.loc/443-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4242, 1, '2017-03-17 11:34:42', '2017-03-17 11:34:42', '[spb_row parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="199" image_size="medium" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="no" lightbox="yes" link_target="_self" width="1/4" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="3/4" el_position="last"]\r\n\r\n[dropcap1]A[/dropcap1]t VIMMI, we’ve built a better network—one that is specially tuned for the rigorous demands of video delivery.Our content delivery network (CDN) is designed for the millions of users who demand a high-quality video experience. Other CDNs install very small servers at thousands of locations, a technique that worked when most users surfed among small HTML files over poor connections.\r\n\r\nToday, both the supply of content and demand for it have exploded. So we’ve developed new methodology that is ideal for the new world of high-speed connections and rich video content. We’ve selected a smaller number of strategic global locations among the primary Internet Exchange Points, and built supercharged points of presence we call VIMMI GigaPOPs. These GigaPOPs have massive numbers of 10Gbps throughput servers and are directly connected to all major backbone networks.\r\n\r\nThe VIMMI network features unique architecture as well as global reach that is based on direct optical fiber connections to over 1,200 ISPs worldwide. It supports a full in-cloud solution for flat-fee OTT as well as an easy-to-operate fee-for-service model. The VIMMI platform provides 99.9999% network availability at extremely low set-up costs and with virtually no capital investment. Just choose the system elements that you need to complete your solution and VIMMI will provide them on a full-managed service basis.is text.\r\n\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]', 'VIMMI GLOBAL NETWORK', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '230-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:34:42', '2017-03-17 11:34:42', '', 230, 'http://vimmi.loc/230-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4243, 1, '2017-03-17 11:35:20', '2017-03-17 11:35:20', '[boxed_content type="coloured" custom_bg_colour="#ffffff" custom_text_colour="#000000" pb_margin_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">VOD Streaming</h3>\r\nUpsell your valuable video assets with efficient, personalized and cost-effective VOD streaming services. Using the Vimmi Media Delivery Platform, you can stream personalized content to viewers from cloud-based Vimmi video storage and caching servers. Scalable and distributed broadcast-grade platform architecture grows with your business and with asset volume, so you pay only for what you need, when you need it—and never get caught short if demand suddenly spikes.\r\n\r\nVimmi VOD services integrate easily with leading subscriber billing and management systems to support pay-per-view, ad-supported and subscription based VOD consumption across multiple devices and screens.\r\n\r\nSocial tools can be integrated to enhance user interactivity and grow both the subscriber base and usage among existing subscribers.\r\n\r\nVIMMI cloud-based transcoding-as-a-service creates file-based assets for adaptive streaming. Save on transcoding expenses, free up storage space and make it easier and less costly to manage video assets by streaming HDS, HLS, HSS, DASH and RTSP.\r\n\r\n[/boxed_content] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]', 'VOD Streaming', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '252-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:35:20', '2017-03-17 11:35:20', '', 252, 'http://vimmi.loc/252-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4244, 1, '2017-03-17 11:38:53', '2017-03-17 11:38:53', '<div class="OkjkmFj">who will <a href="https://meowessay.com/">write me an essay</a> no plagiarism</div>\r\n[spb_row parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<h3><a href="http://vimmi.loc/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/inner_page_video.png"><img class=" size-full wp-image-209 aligncenter" src="http://vimmi.loc/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/inner_page_video.png" alt="inner_page_video" width="924" height="177" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3>WHITE LABEL CDN / LICENSED CDN FOR ISP’S AND TELCO OPERATORS</h3>\r\nWith video dominating Internet usage and consumers shifting their viewing from TV screens to a diverse array of Internet-connected screens, video service providers and ISPs increasingly need to provide efficient, high performance video CDN services if they want to stay in the game. And affordable, broadcast-quality video delivery over unmanaged networks serves as an attractive differentiation opportunity in the competitive and largely undifferentiated service provider industry.\r\n\r\nCDNs are notoriously challenging to build and operate: Long development horizons and deployment processes, together with rapidly evolving technology and formats make developing an in-house video CDN from scratch extremely costly, in terms of both time and cash. In fact, many video CDNs end up being obsolete even before they are completed.\r\n\r\nSystem integrators lack the combined expertise in video and IP that is needed to create a robust, flexible and cost-effective video delivery network that can reliably stream vast amounts of content at broadcast quality. Few are able to achieve the scale that allows service providers to cost-effectively deliver video to remote points on the globe.\r\n\r\nMany video service providers and ISPs have opted to outsource video delivery to global CDNs rather than creating networks in-house. However, global CDNs have little experience and less expertise in video delivery. They can not provide the granularity and control that are essential for ensuring that premium video is reliably delivered to every subscriber screen at broadcast quality.\r\n\r\nWhen it comes to video delivery, smart service providers leave CDN to the video CDN experts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Two models for fast CDN deployment for service providers</strong>\r\n\r\nNow, VIMMI empowers ISPs and video service providers to quickly and confidently deploy broadcast quality video delivery services for their clients, without costly and risky in-house CDN development. VIMMI offers two models to meet the need of all service providers:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>White-label. VIMMI is pleased to offer CDN services that operate entirely under the branding of our service provider clients. <a class="more-link" href="http://vimmi.loc/Video.CDN/Licensed.CDN.for.ISPs.and.Telco.Operators/White.label.video.CDN">Read more</a></li>\r\n	<li>Licensing. Under this model, VIMMI provides the service provider with code that enables them to create and fully operate a broadcast-quality CDN in-house. <a class="more-link" href="http://vimmi.loc/Video.CDN/Licensed.CDN.for.ISPs.and.Telco.Operators/Licensed.video.CDN">Read more</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]', 'WHITE LABEL CDN / LICENSED', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '293-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:38:53', '2017-03-17 11:38:53', '', 293, 'http://vimmi.loc/293-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4245, 1, '2017-03-17 11:39:31', '2017-03-17 11:39:31', '[spb_row parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<h3><a href="http://vimmi.loc/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/inner_page_video.png"><img class=" size-full wp-image-209 aligncenter" src="http://vimmi.loc/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/inner_page_video.png" alt="inner_page_video" width="924" height="177" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3>WHITE LABEL CDN / LICENSED CDN FOR ISP’S AND TELCO OPERATORS</h3>\r\nWith video dominating Internet usage and consumers shifting their viewing from TV screens to a diverse array of Internet-connected screens, video service providers and ISPs increasingly need to provide efficient, high performance video CDN services if they want to stay in the game. And affordable, broadcast-quality video delivery over unmanaged networks serves as an attractive differentiation opportunity in the competitive and largely undifferentiated service provider industry.\r\n\r\nCDNs are notoriously challenging to build and operate: Long development horizons and deployment processes, together with rapidly evolving technology and formats make developing an in-house video CDN from scratch extremely costly, in terms of both time and cash. In fact, many video CDNs end up being obsolete even before they are completed.\r\n\r\nSystem integrators lack the combined expertise in video and IP that is needed to create a robust, flexible and cost-effective video delivery network that can reliably stream vast amounts of content at broadcast quality. Few are able to achieve the scale that allows service providers to cost-effectively deliver video to remote points on the globe.\r\n\r\nMany video service providers and ISPs have opted to outsource video delivery to global CDNs rather than creating networks in-house. However, global CDNs have little experience and less expertise in video delivery. They can not provide the granularity and control that are essential for ensuring that premium video is reliably delivered to every subscriber screen at broadcast quality.\r\n\r\nWhen it comes to video delivery, smart service providers leave CDN to the video CDN experts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Two models for fast CDN deployment for service providers</strong>\r\n\r\nNow, VIMMI empowers ISPs and video service providers to quickly and confidently deploy broadcast quality video delivery services for their clients, without costly and risky in-house CDN development. VIMMI offers two models to meet the need of all service providers:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>White-label. VIMMI is pleased to offer CDN services that operate entirely under the branding of our service provider clients. <a class="more-link" href="http://vimmi.loc/Video.CDN/Licensed.CDN.for.ISPs.and.Telco.Operators/White.label.video.CDN">Read more</a></li>\r\n	<li>Licensing. Under this model, VIMMI provides the service provider with code that enables them to create and fully operate a broadcast-quality CDN in-house. <a class="more-link" href="http://vimmi.loc/Video.CDN/Licensed.CDN.for.ISPs.and.Telco.Operators/Licensed.video.CDN">Read more</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]', 'WHITE LABEL CDN / LICENSED', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '293-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:39:31', '2017-03-17 11:39:31', '', 293, 'http://vimmi.loc/293-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4246, 1, '2017-03-17 11:40:41', '2017-03-17 11:40:41', '[spb_row parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="1264" image_size="medium" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="no" lightbox="yes" link_target="_self" width="1/4" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="3/4" el_position="last"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">WHITE LABEL VIDEO CDN</h3>\r\nFor service providers that prefer to outsource video CDN service operations—but still want to offer those services under their own brand--VIMMI is pleased to provide comprehensive white label CDN services. Under the white-label program, VIMMI owns and operates the CDN for the service provider on our own hardware platform and all services are provided under the service provider’s brand.\r\n\r\nFirst level support is provided by the ISP or video service provider, but VIMMI handles more complex service issues. VIMMI also offers optional assistance with sales, system engineering and structuring the video CDN business.\r\n\r\n<strong>Advantages of VIMMI white label video CDN</strong>\r\n\r\nVIMMI video CDN is the best white label service for delivering video over managed and unmanaged networks. As specialists in video CDN, VIMMI has an impressive track record of success. Our hard-earned expertise translates into higher QoS, greater control of your network and more opportunities to monetize network resources.\r\n\r\nVIMMI assists its white label clients in acquiring the skill set needed to promote CDNs through business rules, pricing and business engineering.\r\n\r\nVIMMI white label CDN users benefit from:\r\n[list]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Offering profitable and relevant new services to existing clients [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Designed-for-video CDN platform [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Proven best-of-breed technology that delivers high QoS [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] 24x7x365 NOC [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Real time analytics and reporting [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Fastest time-to-market [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Support for emerging standards, formats and viewing platforms [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] LowOPEX [/list_item]\r\n[list_item icon="ss-check"] Expert guidance in building a strong, viable content delivery business [/list_item]\r\n[/list]\r\n\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]', 'WHITE LABEL VIDEO CDN', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '300-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:40:41', '2017-03-17 11:40:41', '', 300, 'http://vimmi.loc/300-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4247, 1, '2017-03-17 11:41:24', '2017-03-17 11:41:24', '[spb_row wrap_type="full-width" parallax_type="color" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="30" row_margin_vertical="30" remove_element_spacing="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="1260" image_size="full" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="yes" lightbox="no" link_target="_self" width="1/3" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="2/3" el_position="last"]\r\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">VIMMI, the technology leader in distributed video delivery network platforms, has designed a suite of video services that empower content owners and operators to fully monetize their video assets. These services include the VIMMI global video Content Delivery Network (CDN), in-cloud content preparation services, a modular in-cloud <em>Back Office &amp; Video Monetization Suite</em> and a ready-to-use <em>OTT-as-a-service</em> solution.</p>\r\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">For ISP’s and Telecom operators we are pleased to provide <em>white label global video CDN</em>. So now you can run your business and focus on marketing and maximizing your profits while VIMMI manages CDN services for you and assumes full responsibility for all infrastructure and operations. If at any time you wish to switch to your own CDN platform, VIMMI will gladly license the system to you to ensure a seamless transition.</p>\r\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">The global CDN service is based on a technology platform designed and developed by VIMMI. VIMMI is committed to creating advanced solutions that efficiently address the challenges of equipping networks for the future.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row] [spb_row wrap_type="full-width" row_bg_color="#eaf4f6" parallax_type="color" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="30" row_margin_vertical="30" remove_element_spacing="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_single_image image="1260" image_size="full" frame="noframe" intro_animation="flip" full_width="yes" lightbox="no" link_target="_self" width="1/3" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="2/3" el_position="last"]\r\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">VIMMI was founded by visionaries who foresaw the multi-platform, anywhere, anytime video future and were committed to making that future easily accessible to any content owner, service provider, enterprise or public organization.</p>\r\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">VIMMI is realizing its mission with innovative, <em><strong>comprehensive</strong></em> built-for-video network architecture technologies that provide cloud-based video services and broadcast-quality delivery services across managed and unmanaged networks. VIMMI enables its customers to reach any screen, at any time, with any content from any location in the world and to maximize return on their valuable video assets.</p>\r\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">As pioneers in video and IP integration, the company’s founders and leaders are natives in a technology landscape where many players from the video and IP worlds are still learning the basic terrain. The VIMMI solution reflects their experience and expertise.</p>\r\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">Since 2009, the VIMMI platform has provided a full suite of cloud-based, modular service provider-grade video preparation, delivery and management services. An open platform that is integrated via APIs, it is uniquely fast and easy to set up, freeing clients from the complex, costly and delay-prone process of building in-house video processing systems.</p>\r\n<p class="  animated fadeInDown eds-on-scroll fall-p1 ">VIMMI also provides robust, turnkey white label CDN services for video and internet service providers, enabling them to rapidly add advanced OTT delivery to their service offerings without burdensome investments in infrastructure and manpower.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row]', 'WHY VIMMI?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '492-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:41:24', '2017-03-17 11:41:24', '', 492, 'http://vimmi.loc/492-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4260, 1, '2017-03-18 02:56:28', '2017-03-18 02:56:28', 'Saguna and Vimmi Partner to Create Video Delivery Network Solution based on Multi-access Edge Computing \r\n\r\n\r\n<B>Joint MEC solution accelerating video delivery will be showcased at #MWC17</B>\r\n<p>Yokneam, Israel, February 5th, 2017 –<a href="http://www.saguna.net/?utm_source=PR?utm_medium=adlink-partnership?utm_campaign=Q1-2016" target="_blank">Saguna</a>, the Multi-access Edge Computing (MEC) pioneer making mobile broadband faster, simpler and more economical, and <a href="http://vimmi.loc">Vimmi</a>, the mobile video delivery innovator announced today a partnership to bring to market a Content Delivery solution for mobile operators based on the Multi-access Edge Computing (MEC) standard. The joint solution features Vimmi Mobile Delivery Network (MDN) and Saguna Open-RAN MEC platform.</p>\r\n<p>Mobile networks are becoming video networks.  With video playing the leading role in terms of traffic and subscriber volumes, Mobile Operators need a scalable solution to deliver high-quality, immersive video experiences. By deploying video services at the radio edge, in close proximity to mobile users, MEC enables the deployment of a powerful video delivery infrastructure for mobile networks.</p>\r\n<p>The joint solution from Vimmi and Saguna address this market opportunity. The Saguna Open-RAN MEC platform that creates an open ecosystem for 3rd party applications inside mobile Radio Access Network (RAN). The ETSI MEC standard-based solution enables mobile operators to quickly and effectively deploy new revenue-generating services for Internet-of-things (IoT), cyber security, virtual probes, content delivery and augmented reality applications.</p>\r\n<p>Integrated with the Saguna Open-RAN MEC platform, Vimmi’s MDN solution uses grid computing and machine learning technologies that enables delivery of premium video quality at a dramatically lower operational cost. The solution reduces 70%-90% of mobile backhaul traffic while improving QoE. It reduces Round Trip Time for Video and IoT Applications achieving 5G performance targets in 4G networks.</p>\r\n<p>“Mobile Edge Computing is an emerging standard that helps Mobile operators to meet the growing consumer demand for economical, high-quality video experiences.  By integrating Saguna’s Multi-access Edge Computing solution with our video-aware Mobile Delivery Network, we are delivering a critical step-change in mobile video transport performance”, said Eitan Koter, Co. CEO and Founder, Vimmi. “As video streaming continues to grow and becomes significantly more important to service providers’ business, mobile operators will be looking for the best-in-class technologies that can give them an edge. I believe that the Saguna and Vimmi collaboration is going to be provide them with that edge; the combination of the highest possible video delivery efficiency and video performance.”</p>\r\n<p>Commenting on the integration, Saguna CTO Danny Frydman said, “The accelerated growth of video over mobile networks makes Multi-access Edge Computing a crucial addition to mobile networks infrastructure in existing 4G networks and future 5G ones. We are very pleased to join forces with Vimmi on bringing to market highly-effective MEC-based video delivery solutions mobile networks. ” </p>\r\n<B>See it in action in MWC17</B>\r\n<p>The companies will showcase their MEC-based solution featuring Saguna Open-RAN MEC platform and Vimmi MDN at the upcoming Mobile World Congress. </p>\r\n<p>Mobile World Congress will take place in Barcelona, Spain, scheduled for February 27 – March 2, 2017. The demonstrations will be held at Saguna’s booth #5E81 and Vimmi’s booth #5D81. To schedule your personal demo click here.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<B>About Saguna </B>\r\n<p>Saguna Networks, a pioneer of Mobile Edge Computing (MEC), makes mobile broadband faster, simpler and more economical with smart NFV software solutions. Based on the ETSI MEC standard, the Saguna Open-RAN platform enables mobile operators to quickly and effectively deploy new revenue generating services. The Mobile Edge Computing platform has a fully virtualized software architecture providing cost effective scalability and flexibility. For more information contact us at <a href="mailto:info@saguna.net">info@saguna.net</a>, follow us <a href="https://twitter.com/sagunanet">@sagunanet</a> or visit our website www.saguna.net.</p>\r\n\r\n<B>About Vimmi</B>\r\nVimmi was founded by visionaries who foresaw the multi-platform, anywhere, anytime video future and were committed to making that future easily accessible to any content owner, service provider, enterprise or public organization.\r\nVimmi is realizing its mission with innovative, comprehensive built-for-video network architecture technologies that provide virtualized video services and broadcast-quality delivery services across managed and unmanaged networks. Vimmi enables its customers to reach any screen, at any time, with any content from any location in the world and to maximize return on their valuable video assets. For more information contact us at <a href="mailto:info@saguna.net">info@vimmi.loc</a>, or visit our website www.vimmi.loc.\r\n\r\nContact:\r\nTally Netzer\r\nMarketing Director, Saguna\r\nEmail: tally@saguna.net\r\nPhone: +972-4-675-3700\r\n\r\n', 'Saguna and Vimmi Partner to Create Video Delivery Network Solution based on Multi-access Edge Computing', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'saguna-and-vimmi-partner-to-create-video-delivery-network-solution-based-on-multi-access-edge-computing', '', '', '2017-03-18 03:15:38', '2017-03-18 03:15:38', '', 0, 'http://vimmi.loc/?p=4260', 0, 'post', '', 0),
