(4362, 1, '2017-04-11 05:19:59', '2017-04-11 05:19:59', 'Vimmi provide global video CDN and other cloud-based video OTT services such as Content Management System, Billing and Cloud DVR.\r\n\r\nOur cloud technology platform – SOLO - provides a single workflow that enables faster content preparation, global delivery and monetization of video, while meeting today’s pricing pressures.\r\n\r\nVimmi video CDN:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A global CDN built for video from day 1. The cornerstone of our architecture is our ‘CDN-in-a-box’ which can be deployed very fast in locations around the globe to eliminate peering problems and reduce cost.</li>\r\n<li>Future proof – supports 4K video, VOD, live and linear channels over Adaptive Bit Rate (HLS, HDS, RTMP, RTSP) and MPEG DASH.</li>\r\n<li>Supports network DVR and recording of live events, creation of linear channels in our cloud.</li>\r\n<li>1 unified analytics and reporting tools for all technologies and screens</li>\r\n<li>Innovative Business models\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>For content providers - service agreements based on Vimmi global cloud </li>\r\n<li>For Service Providers / Telco’s - Provide software to companies interested in operating video CDN projects based on Vimmi''s technology. </li>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>HTML 5 video player</li>\r\n<li>24x7x365 instant support.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Vimmi Solo OTT', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'vimmi-solo-ott', '', '', '2017-05-05 04:01:26', '2017-05-05 04:01:26', '', 0, 'http://vimmi.loc/?p=4362', 0, 'post', '', 0),
